### **Why This Approach Works**
- Q11 has **low GROUP BY cardinality** (~8,685 unique partkeys out of 2M possible)
- Open-addressing trades **space for speed** — uses 2.7x more memory but gains 2-5x lookup speed
- With 64 CPU cores and 376 GB RAM, memory is abundant; performance is critical
- Avoids failures from prior iterations (3, 7, 8) which attempted different strategies

